c: 5
v: 18
t: "Ne abayahudi nende abakiristo baboola mbu; “efwe khuli Abana ba Nyasaye nende abahelwa bebe” Boola mbu “Ne shichila shina nabahelesinjia eshinyasio khulwetsimbii tsienyu?. Halali enywe mulisa Abandu mubayaloonga, Aleshela owayenya ne ahelesia eshinyasio wayenya. Ne ni bwa Nyasaye obwami bwomwikulu nende khushialo nende bili hakari wabio. Ne amakalushilo ni ewuwe butswa"